{"title":"Salsa tunes up the Timberjack hardtail w/ Alternator 2.0 dropouts, new geo, SS & more","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/25/salsa-tunes-up-the-timberjack-hardtail-w-alternator-2-0-dropouts-new-geo-ss-more/","date":1614269171000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Salsa Cycles is back with an updated Timberjack with plenty of options. Aiming to create a versatile aggressive trail hardtail, the new Timberjack includes an all new frame with a bunch of updates to make the bike more fun on the trail – and also more versatile.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Timberjack hardtail frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"716\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5-297x177.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5-800x477.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-fra