0-dropouts5-1068x637.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts5-704x420.jpg 704w\"></a></p><p>Starting with an aluminum frame that’s meant for 120-150mm travel suspension forks, and features the addition of Alternator 2.0 dropouts.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Timberjack hardtail alternator 2.0 dropouts\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1005\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-297x249.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-800x670.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-768x643.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-696x583.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-1068x894.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-501x420.jpg 501w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-297x249.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-800x670.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-768x643.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-696x583.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-1068x894.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-2021-updated-aluminum-frame-Alternator-2.0-dropouts3-501x420.jpg 501w\"></a></p><p>The previous Timberjack also offered adjustable dropouts, but the Alternator 2.0 system is a bit cleaner than the original Alternators. Thanks to the ability to adjust chainstay length from 420-437mm, single speed is still an option – and Salsa is even selling complete bikes with SS builds.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Timberjack hardtail 2021 geometry\" width=\"559\" height=\"571\" sizes=\"(max-width: 559px) 100vw, 559px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021.jpg 559w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-294x300.jpg 294w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-117x120.jpg 117w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-411x420.jpg 411w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-356x364.jpg 356w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021.jpg 559w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-294x300.jpg 294w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-117x120.jpg 117w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-411x420.jpg 411w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-geometry-2021-356x364.jpg 356w\"></a></p><p>Designed around a new progressive trail geometry, the bike is typically longer, lower, and slacker. Given the fact that the bike can be set up in many different configurations with different wheel, tire, and suspension fork sizes, these numbers a likely to vary slightly based on the set up. But when running a 130mm travel fork and either 27.5 x 3.0″ or 29 x 2.4″ tires, the geometry includes a 75.1° seat tube angle, 66.35° head tube angle, and longer reach numbers to work with short stems and wide bars (note that the geometry chart lists 27.5 x 3.0″ tires, but the claimed tire clearance below tops out at 27.5 x 2.8″).</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Timberjack hardtail complete bike\" width=\"1200\" height=\"932\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-297x231.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-800x621.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-120x93.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-768x596.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-696x541.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-1068x829.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-541x420.jpg 541w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-297x231.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-800x621.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-120x93.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-768x596.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-696x541.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-1068x829.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-models-single-speed-complete3-541x420.jpg 541w\"></a></p><p>Salsa gave the Timberjack tire clearance for up to 29 x 2.6 or 27.5 x 2.8″ rubber – and there are complete bikes that come in both wheel sizes. Stock bikes will include either 29 x 2.6″ or 27.5 x 2.8″ Maxxis tires.</p><p>You’ll also find updated internal cable routing and a straight seat tube for longer dropper post use.</p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-bikepacking-dropper-post-new-frame1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-bikepacking-dropper-post-new-frame1.jpg\" alt=\"Salsa Timberjack hardtail accessory mounts\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-bikepacking-dropper-post-new-frame1.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-bikepacking-dropper-post-new-frame1.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Salsa-Timberjack-mountain-bike-2021-bikepacking-dropper-post-new-frame1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/upload